{"tid":2273836,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英外相：屢促中方公平待12港人","createTime":"2020-11-06T04:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T13:27:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f4eaae03a7edf9494b6cf774a396411b8e619d20","tid":2273836,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/FQTFRN25HBHPDBPVJPWJC4XKGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FFQTFRN25HBHPDBPVJPWJC4XKGU%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8ooP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=be664890\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FFQTFRN25HBHPDBPVJPWJC4XKGU%2F&h=7981ecb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/FQTFRN25HBHPDBPVJPWJC4XKGU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n英外相：屢促中方公平待12港人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S1bKtB8c21N9y5DY9RVQYGMuxxk=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2X56BOO2V5BKNIU7GYO5PLMZ4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS1bKtB8c21N9y5DY9RVQYGMuxxk%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2X56BOO2V5BKNIU7GYO5PLMZ4A.jpg&h=f349385f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■英國外相藍韜文回信國會議員，表明繼續關注12名被扣內地港人情況。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12名港青8月疑偷渡台灣遭內地截獲，扣押至今音訊全無。英國外相藍韜文回覆關注12港人的英國上議院議員奧爾頓勳爵（Lord Alton of Liverpool )時指，深切關注事件及12人被扣押的情況，又指在多個場合已向特區和中國官員表示關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：司法局加壓「監督」港青律師  要求接委託須報備 恐嚇合夥人退出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指英官員有聯絡家屬代表<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文回覆奧爾頓勳爵時表明，深切關注事件及12港人被扣押情況，尤其是事件對香港高度自治和自由的影響，藍韜文又提及英國駐港和駐京的高級官員，曾在數個場合向特區和中國官員表示關注事件，促請他們一定要跟足正當法律程序，英國政府將來會繼續有關做法。確保被捕人士獲公平對待，並指英方官員亦與12港人家屬的立法會代表保持聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n雖然12港人中有人擁有BNO，不過藍韜文在回覆指出，英國。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文重申，《中英聯合聲明》保障香港人的權利及自由，眼看有關權利以及自由被侵蝕，。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"6e61c8e5ade63b1eae3e241aad724ef3229ca2aa","tid":2273836,"uid":282930,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:39:52.000Z","msg":"收返算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3fe2a76038fde479522ab1a1f9d1edf90e61e4","tid":2273836,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4411baf39e56e513eb6a25177264bcb643d496d","tid":2273836,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:04:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e782fd5e976750c3027b9669e9261f5f8ba6d3b8","tid":2273836,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:05:53.000Z","msg":"12個真係咩消息都冇"},{"pid":"a3d813d57d3c715e3e0a3c324da5daa42eafb624","tid":2273836,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"持續關注，保持熱度，快d俾港人回港"}]}